# Prompt Protection (SACRED)

## Non-negotiable rule

All prompt files under `prompts/` contain critical business intelligence and must **never** be edited, rewritten, reformatted, or “improved”.

### Prohibited changes

- Do **not** modify any `.md` prompt in `prompts/`.
- Do **not** override or monkeypatch vendor prompt templates at runtime.

### Allowed work

- You may **assess** prompts for risks (length, ambiguity, conflicting instructions) and recommend non-code operational fixes.
- You may adjust **code/config** so the system uses the prompts correctly (without changing prompt text).
